QuestData.Title: Sweet as Honey
QuestData.Description: <The hatchling scampers about, then whines and whimpers.>$B$BFrom the cloud serpent's behavior, you have a hunch that it wants a sweet treat.$B$BThe fragrant trees in The Arboretum are home to many honey hives.$B$BIt will be a simple matter to collect combs from the nearby honeykeepers.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 30 Honeycomb from Angry Honeykeepers in The Arboretum.
